    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/4a8d45e8b59dec90832faaf6d1980143.webp?t=1758057854\" width=127 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/b03307bf59e324edda9c5d0b7d43bed3.poster.avif?t=1758057854\" width=616 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/b03307bf59e324edda9c5d0b7d43bed3.webm?t=1758057854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/b03307bf59e324edda9c5d0b7d43bed3.mp4?t=1758057854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在遭遇船难之后，你发现自己身处一个神秘的岛屿，这个岛屿在任何地图上都没有标记。然而，在这个神秘的岛屿上耸立着一座灯塔——这是我们唯一的救赎之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >云猫是友好而顽皮的生物，热情地欢迎新客人。然而，灯塔的看守者发生了什么事？这些猫咪真的与他的失踪无关吗？  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/b871a47ced68c09ed9faff7c271a1373.webp?t=1758057854\" width=86 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/55a03f6cc7b059050c0c62e04e8f2792.poster.avif?t=1758057854\" width=616 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/55a03f6cc7b059050c0c62e04e8f2792.webm?t=1758057854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/55a03f6cc7b059050c0c62e04e8f2792.mp4?t=1758057854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每只猫咪都是独一无二的，给你的旅程带来了独特的魔力。吸引猫咪来解开谜题，它们会在你难忘的冒险中帮助你。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/30d01c4bad14ed400d43a5fea6b7dc85.webp?t=1758057854\" width=86 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/5e524af886b9e8b5de6ac44daa56d6f8.poster.avif?t=1758057854\" width=616 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/5e524af886b9e8b5de6ac44daa56d6f8.webm?t=1758057854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/5e524af886b9e8b5de6ac44daa56d6f8.mp4?t=1758057854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用你的智慧，与那些在你路上遇到的奇怪生物找到共同语言。谁说深渊生物不喜欢冰淇淋？  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/079fce1cafbedcb4e8931224e7f70ded.webp?t=1758057854\" width=85 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/8b5a0361d8f5baa9c4a9bef432527885.poster.avif?t=1758057854\" width=616 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/8b5a0361d8f5baa9c4a9bef432527885.webm?t=1758057854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/8b5a0361d8f5baa9c4a9bef432527885.mp4?t=1758057854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于最普通的事物，也能找到不寻常的用法。你有一段栅栏吗？为什么不把它变成轨道呢？它们看起来如此相似！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/87aac3639eb6e2acf728337673075d39.webp?t=1758057854\" width=87 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/32f9ecb7fedf37a5d6c8bff07b4f98d9.poster.avif?t=1758057854\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/32f9ecb7fedf37a5d6c8bff07b4f98d9.webm?t=1758057854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239500/extras/32f9ecb7fedf37a5d6c8bff07b4f98d9.mp4?t=1758057854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛上的每一个角落都隐藏着谜团和独特的挑战。利用魔法猫咪解决谜题，进行迷你游戏，探索这个岛屿——也许你将是揭开云猫之谜的人！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
